Specimen Container Preparation and Specimen Collection Event
This message structure supports tracking of information related to preparations for specimen collection and the collection event.
This message structure supports tracking of information when specimen collection is not successful.
This message structure supports tracking of information related to the movements of specimens across locations, and placement in and out of storage.
This message structure supports tracking of information to identify or de-identify specimens or at time of final disposal.
This message structure supports tracking of information related to processing of one or more specimen that may result in derived (child) specimen or not.
This message structure supports tracking of information when the processing of a specimen was unsuccessful.
